	tests/Polyhedron/Makefile.am, tests/Polyhedron/linearexpression1.cc: 
	FIXME resolved.  Fixed a bug in Linear_Expression(Variable v,
	Variable w).  The bug would cause a wrong result to be computed when
	v == w.

